    "templateCredsSetupCompleted": false,
    "description": "LocalClaw follow-up sequence — runs daily at 9AM, queries Supabase for leads with no response in 24+ hours, sends up to 3 follow-up messages via WhatsApp, updates lead status, and escalates to owner on the 3rd unanswered follow-up."
